    <description>A voice-enabled productivity agent for sales reps to manage their projects hands-free between meetings, in the car, or right after a customer interaction. The agent provides quick verbal summaries of project status, key dates, owner, recent activities, and open risks, and updates project records on request — including shifting start or end dates, logging notes, and capturing follow-ups. It identifies the calling user via Salesforce context and only acts on projects they own or are assigned to. All write operations require explicit verbal confirmation before committing, and every conversation is logged for audit. Designed for use via Agentforce Voice Preview and PSTN telephony.</description>
